<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="fr"><head><meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Erreur {{ status_code }} — Comité Maoré</title>
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
body{font-family:'Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif;background:linear-gradient(160deg,#0f1117,#1a202c);
color:#e2e8f0;min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
.box{background:rgba(45,55,72,.8);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-radius:16px;
padding:48px 40px;max-width:520px;width:90%;text-align:center;}
.code{font-size:96px;font-weight:800;color:#68d391;line-height:1;margin-bottom:8px;letter-spacing:-4px;}
.titre{font-size:22px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px;}
.desc{font-size:14px;color:#a0aec0;margin-bottom:32px;line-height:1.6;}
.btn{display:inline-block;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;margin:4px;}
.btn-p{background:#276749;color:#9ae6b4;}
.btn-s{background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);color:#e2e8f0;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);}
.brand{font-size:13px;color:#4a5568;margin-bottom:32px;}
.brand strong{color:#68d391;}
</style></head>
<body><div class="box">
<div class="brand"><strong>Comité Maoré</strong></div>
<div class="code">{{ status_code }}</div>
<div class="titre">{{ status_text }}</div>
<p class="desc">Une erreur est survenue lors du traitement de votre demande.</p>
<div>
<a href="/" class="btn btn-p">🏠 Retour à l'accueil</a>
<a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn btn-s">← Page précédente</a>
</div>
</div></body></html>
